.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, teacher
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, swimming
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, tram
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the doctor##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
4. the doctor is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby      | hiking      | writing     |
| Job   | teacher    | doctor  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Sport         | climbing | swimming |
| Transport     | ship     | tram     |

 